  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a37a916b0ee223c9122b92c",
      "text": "choi-draw",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782032663,
      "updated": 1782032663
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37a91600000000000d81a8",
      "text": "from [2026/06/20]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782032663,
      "updated": 1782032663
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37a94c0000000000cabc98",
      "text": "[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782032716,
      "updated": 1782032724
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37a91600000000000d81a9",
      "text": "[https://inajob.github.io/choi-draw/ choi-draw]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782032663,
      "updated": 1782032663
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37a91600000000000d81aa",
      "text": "\tつくったよ！",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782032663,
      "updated": 1782032663
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37a91600000000000d81ab",
      "text": "\t画像に「ちょい」と矢印と文字を挿入するだけのWebツール",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782032663,
      "updated": 1782032663
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37a91600000000000d81ac",
      "text": "\tすっごい[Windows98]みを感じるUI[takker.icon][Hiro Aki.icon][koyoshi.icon]",
      "userId": "6606ca1148e7150024f0f07d",
      "created": 1782032663,
      "updated": 1782119133
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37a91600000000000d81ad",
      "text": "\tホイホイされる[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782032663,
      "updated": 1782032663
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37a91600000000000d81ae",
      "text": "\t良いなあ[はるひ.icon][caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782032663,
      "updated": 1782032663
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37a91600000000000d81af",
      "text": "\t画像の解像度に依存して矢印や文字のサイズが変わったように見えてしまう問題を直そう",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782032663,
      "updated": 1782032663
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37a91600000000000d81b0",
      "text": "\t 対応したが今度は大きすぎかな？",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782032663,
      "updated": 1782032663
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37a91600000000000d81b1",
      "text": "\t[https://gyazo.com/1b3f5d8af1c2b1c401768399237c9c8f]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782032663,
      "updated": 1782032663
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37a9fb0000000000cabc9c",
      "text": "\t  [たんぽぽ]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782032891,
      "updated": 1782032897
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37a91600000000000d81b2",
      "text": "  ヨシ！",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782032663,
      "updated": 1782032663
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37a91600000000000d81b3",
      "text": "  どれか１つ「[たんぼぼ]」とかになってる間違い探しかな？と思って真剣に見てしまった。ひねくれた性格していて申し訳ありません[Hiro Aki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782032663,
      "updated": 1782032876
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37a91600000000000d81b4",
      "text": "  狂気[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782032663,
      "updated": 1782032663
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37a91600000000000d81b5",
      "text": "  おんなじテキスト気軽にめっちゃ貼れるのたのしい[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782032663,
      "updated": 1782032663
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37a91600000000000d81b6",
      "text": " これ思い出した[terang.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782032663,
      "updated": 1782032663
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37a91600000000000d81b7",
      "text": " \t>[https://x.com/toritori_gt/status/1302508627786260480 @toritori_gt]: 知識があることと不思議に思う感性があると見てる世界が変わる。",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782032663,
      "updated": 1782032663
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37a91600000000000d81b8",
      "text": "  >[https://gyazo.com/7b57efe8946a14a913d17c35983c9e89][https://gyazo.com/f2caf963d21aa21c5e892ae81d748dd5]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782032663,
      "updated": 1782032663
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37a91600000000000d81b9",
      "text": "   [霧立越]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782032663,
      "updated": 1782032663
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37a91600000000000d81ba",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782032663,
      "updated": 1782032663
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37a9410000000000cabc81",
      "text": "from [2026/06/20]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782032705,
      "updated": 1782032705
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37a9670000000000cabc99",
      "text": "のりしろ [ご同伴に預かる#6a37a9a50000000000a3d79c]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782032743,
      "updated": 1782032864
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37a96a0000000000cabc9a",
      "text": "> 果物を食べているとコバエがやってきてご同伴に預かろうとしてくる",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782032746,
      "updated": 1782032749
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37a96c0000000000cabc9b",
      "text": ">   やめてほしい",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782032749,
      "updated": 1782032749
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37a9410000000000cabc82",
      "text": "[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782032705,
      "updated": 1782032712
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37a9410000000000cabc83",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/f539d1b4035eee041999e68b7980787f]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782032705,
      "updated": 1782032705
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37a9410000000000cabc84",
      "text": " [ガリ]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782032705,
      "updated": 1782032872
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37a9410000000000cabc85",
      "text": " 早速有効利用してて良い[Hiro Aki.icon][inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782032705,
      "updated": 1782032705
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37a9410000000000cabc86",
      "text": " 画像めっちゃでかそう[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782032705,
      "updated": 1782032705
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37a9410000000000cabc87",
      "text": " \t文字サイズは変更できないと思っていて、かつ結構でかい",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782032705,
      "updated": 1782032705
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37a9410000000000cabc88",
      "text": " \t文字がここまで小さいので、元の画像めっちゃでかそうだなと思った。3000pixelくらいはありそう",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782032705,
      "updated": 1782032705
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37a9410000000000cabc89",
      "text": " \t4032×3024だった[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782032705,
      "updated": 1782032705
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37a9410000000000cabc8a",
      "text": " \tそうか、最近の？スマホってサイズでかい可能性がある[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782032705,
      "updated": 1782032705
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37a9410000000000cabc8b",
      "text": " \t\t[4032x3024は普通]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782032705,
      "updated": 1782032705
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37a9410000000000cabc8c",
      "text": " コバエがいるのかと思って拡大してしまった[yosider.icon][nyarla.icon][koyoshi.icon]",
      "userId": "6606ca1148e7150024f0f07d",
      "created": 1782032705,
      "updated": 1782119096
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37a9410000000000cabc8d",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/565a4edcc5d5924cd1ff2df46c378086]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782032705,
      "updated": 1782032705
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37a9410000000000cabc8e",
      "text": "  いいかんじだ！[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782032705,
      "updated": 1782032705
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37a9410000000000cabc8f",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/b341601024fa92dfc26207b5fa3ea8fe][takker.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782032705,
      "updated": 1782032705
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37a9410000000000cabc90",
      "text": " got itと脳内変換して読んでも趣があるｗ[terang.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782032705,
      "updated": 1782032705
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37a9410000000000cabc91",
      "text": "  This is gari.[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782032705,
      "updated": 1782032705
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37a9410000000000cabc92",
      "text": "   got it...",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782032705,
      "updated": 1782032705
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37a9410000000000cabc93",
      "text": "    got it...",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782032705,
      "updated": 1782032705
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37a9410000000000cabc94",
      "text": "     got it...",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782032705,
      "updated": 1782032705
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37a9410000000000cabc95",
      "text": "  皆から理解されるガリ[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782032705,
      "updated": 1782032705
    },
    {
      "id": "6a37a9410000000000cabc96",
      "text": " w[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1782032705,
      "updated": 1782032705
    },
